Tilesize: 
//This is governs the size of the tile for the tileSet and the map.
1-4) 32

#Tiles-X:
//This is the X length of the map

#Tiles-Y:
//This is the Y length of the map (vertical)

Spacing:
//This is the spacing between tiles.
//The onle of the sample URLS that has a spacing is #3

Isometric?: 
//1,t,true all yield true
//anything else yields false

***************************************
Controls
***************************************

Selection Rectangle - w,a,s,d to resize the rectangle to select a bigger portion of the sorce image.

Layer Select - 1,2 (above qwerty) to flip between the available layers.

Drag and draw - hold shift and mouse over to draw with the top left.
